\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces Architecture of the proposed lightweight hybrid ensemble for WAF threat detection. Four-stage pipeline: (Stage 1) horizontal data processing flow—raw network flows through preprocessing, feature selection (SelectKBest, k=30), SMOTE balancing (k=5 neighbors), and train-test split (80/20); (Stage 2) parallel training of three diverse learners—KNN (k=5), Random Forest (n=100), and XGBoost (n=50); (Stage 3) weighted soft-voting ensemble with weights [0.2, 0.4, 0.4]; (Stage 4) final binary classification (Normal/Attack) with per-dataset and per-class evaluation metrics.}}{3}{}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:architecture}{{1}{3}{}{figure.1}{}}
